{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581", "id": 928539794, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU5Mjg1Mzk3OTQ=", "number": 86581, "title": "`cargo fix --broken-code` incorrectly applies integer casts", "user": {"login": "Jess3Jane", "id": 4605927, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ2MDU5Mjc=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4605927?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane", "html_url": "https://github.com/Jess3Jane", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Jess3Jane/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2021-06-23T18:40:25Z", "updated_at": "2021-06-23T19:25:54Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Consider the following:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn foo(_: u32) {}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let v: usize = 10;\r\n    foo(v)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n`cargo fix --broken-code` correctly notices that this code is broken, but it incorrectly applies the fix:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn foo(_: u32) {}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let v: usize = 10;\r\n    foo(v.try_into().unwrap())\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt applies the `try_into` but doesn't import `std::convert::TryInto`, causing the fix to fail\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.52.1 (9bc8c42bb 2021-05-09)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: 9bc8c42bb2f19e745a63f3445f1ac248fb015e53\r\ncommit-date: 2021-05-09\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nrelease: 1.52.1\r\nLLVM version: 12.0.0\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/86581/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}